    public class DatabaseModuleActivity
extends AuthenticationModuleActivity

    DatabaseModuleActivity

    In the order of ModuleActivities, this one is the third module which it handles Firebase database. It uses Database as an interface and the main job will be done in DatabaseImpl class. But there are some simple usages about this class beside being an interface. For instance when we execute a query on places or comments, here it collects their snapshots when each of them get ready, and in the end we can get those lists from the activities that extend this module.
